title: The Price is Zeit 3/6: SXSW, 538, Rosie the Riveter,  The Way Back, Draymond Green, Kim Kardashian
itunes:title: The Price is Zeit 3/6: SXSW, 538, Rosie the Riveter,  The Way Back, Draymond Green, Kim Kardashian
description:
On this edition of the Price is Zeit Jack, Sophie, and DJ Danl discuss SXSW getting cancelled, a new 538 poll about nomination potential, Rosalind P. Walter - the inspiration for Rosie the Riveter - has passed at the age of 95, the new Ben Affleck movie is....good, Draymond Green is saying some rude things about Charles Barkley, and Kim Kardashian needs some questions answered.
